rdfs:label: A unique token representing this element set. This will be used as the prefix identifying this URI in RDF curies or as a qname in XML
A human-readable descriptive label for the vocab. This will be displayed in lists of vocabs.
The registry code of the status (defaults to published)
A non-Registry URL that contains more information about this element set
A note about this element set
The registry ID of the owner/agent
The registry ID of the vocab admin (must be affiliated with the owner/agent)
RDA agent (person, family, corporate body) properties
is respondent of
skos:definition: Relates a candidate for a degree who defends or opposes a thesis provided by the praeses in an academic disputation to the resource.
reg:name: respondentOf

rdfs:label: is degree granting institution of
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body granting an academic degree to the resource.
reg:name: degreeGrantingInstitutionOf

rdfs:label: is host institution of
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body hosting the event, exhibit, conference, etc., which gave rise to a resource, but having little or no responsibility for the content of the resource to the resource.
reg:name: hostInstitutionOf

rdfs:label: is production company of
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body that is responsible for financial, technical, and organizational management of a production for stage, screen, sound recording, television, webcast, etc. to the resource.
reg:name: productionCompanyOf

rdfs:label: is court governed of
skos:definition: Relates a court governed by court rules, regardless of their official nature (e.g., laws, administrative regulations) to the resource.
reg:name: courtGovernedOf

rdfs:label: is collector of
skos:definition: Relates a curator who brings together items from various sources that are then arranged, described, and cataloged as a collection to the resource.
reg:name: collectorOf

rdfs:label: is collection registrar of
skos:definition: Relates a curator who lists or inventories the items in an aggregate resource such as a collection of items or resources to the resource.
reg:name: collectionRegistrarOf

rdfs:label: is depositor of
skos:definition: Relates a current owner of a resource who deposited the resource into the custody of another person, family, or corporate body, while still retaining ownership to the resource.
reg:name: depositorOf

rdfs:label: is film director of
skos:definition: Relates a director responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance to the resource.
reg:name: filmDirectorOf

rdfs:label: is radio director of
skos:definition: Relates a director responsible for the general management and supervision of a radio program to the resource.
reg:name: radioDirectorOf

rdfs:label: is television director of
skos:definition: Relates a director responsible for the general management and supervision of a television program to the resource.
reg:name: televisionDirectorOf
